com.ca.mas.identity.user

Class MASName

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ca.mas.identity.user.MASName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MASTransformable

    public class MASName
extends java.lang.Object
implements MASTransformable

    The MASName interface contains the common attribute name components of the user's name. Service providers MAY return just the full name as a single string in the formatted sub-attribute, or they MAY return just the individual component attributes using the other sub-attributes, or they MAY return both.

      "name": {
      "formatted": "Ms. Barbara J Jensen, III",
      "familyName": "Jensen",
      "givenName": "Barbara",
      "middleName": "Jane",
      "honorificPrefix": "Ms.",
      "honorificSuffix": "III"
  }
